OL,4,G0000FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,5,     GCraig and his crew tackle Gollen,
OL,6,     Gthe steepest block they've seen,
OL,7,     Gbut storms and a stuck truck halt
OL,8,     Gprogress. Meanwhile, Brent
OL,9,     Gbattles repairs and snowfall
OL,10,     Gwhile clearing a ski trail.
OL,11,G0100FOutback Truckers
OL,12,     GMidway through a vital run Turbo
OL,13,     Gis feeling the temperature as his
OL,14,     Grig overheats. Meanwhile, Mark
OL,15,     GCromwell is fighting to complete
OL,16,     Gthe biggest job of his career.
